OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,FThe maternity unit at Yeovil District
OL,8,FHospital will be closed down
OL,9,Ftemporarily due to concerns for the
OL,10,Fsafety of care for babies and children.
OL,12,FIn a statement the hospital trust said
OL,13,Fit 'cannot currently safely run the
OL,14,Funit' or 'safely provide care during
OL,15,Flabour and birth'.
OL,17,FStaff members say they were told in an
OL,18,Femergency meeting on Tuesday, 13 May
OL,19,Fand Somerset NHS Foundation Trust has
OL,20,Fconfirmed it will close from 5pm on
OL,21,FMonday.
