OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,FThe hospital trust has said the care
OL,8,Fof pregnant women will now be
OL,9,Ftransferred to Musgrove Park Hospital
OL,10,For maternity units in Dorchester or
OL,11,FBath.
OL,13,FThe temporary closure comes after
OL,14,Fmaternity services at the hospital
OL,15,Fwere rated inadequate by the Care
OL,16,FQuality Commission (CQC), last year.
