OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,FAccording to the CQC's report, there
OL,8,Fwas not enough emergency equipment in
OL,9,Fthe unit to safely care for babies,
OL,10,Fand the service didn't always have
OL,11,Fenough medical staff.
OL,13,FIt also found not all staff followed
OL,14,Finfection control principles, like
OL,15,Fwashing their hands before
OL,16,Fadministering care.
