OL,7,FMaternity services at Taunton's
OL,8,FMusgrove Park were similarly rated
OL,9,Finadequate and bosses of both
OL,10,Fhospitals were sent warning notices of
OL,11,Fthe need to improve. The report found
OL,12,Fstaff had failed to complete mandatory
OL,13,Ftraining, with knowledge gaps
OL,14,Fincluding how to manage when unborn
OL,15,Fbabies had reduced movements or growth
OL,16,Frestrictions.
