OL,7,F"The Care Quality Commission inspected
OL,8,Four paediatric services in January and
OL,9,Fissued a Section 29A warning notice
OL,10,Fbecause it assessed that the
OL,11,Fpaediatric care we provide at YDH
OL,12,Frequires significant
OL,14,Fimprovement.
OL,16,F"We also currently have high levels of
OL,17,Fsickness amongst senior paediatricians
OL,18,Fwhich has caused big gaps in our rota.
