OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"Senior paediatricians from Musgrove
OL,8,FPark Hospital are supporting the
OL,9,Fservice at YDH, to ensure that
OL,10,Fpaediatric inpatient and outpatient
OL,11,Fservices at YDH are open for those who
OL,12,Fneed them. However, we are not able to
OL,13,Fsupport the SCBU in the same way and
OL,14,Ftherefore we must close it temporarily
OL,15,Fon safety grounds.
