OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"This directly impacts on the YDH
OL,8,Finpatient maternity service because we
OL,9,Fcannot care for any newborns who
OL,10,Frequire care in a Special Care Baby
OL,11,FUnit or safely provide care during
OL,12,Flabour and birth at the Yeovil
OL,13,FMaternity Unit.
OL,15,F"Most services remain open, and we are
OL,16,Fworking with neighbouring NHS trusts
OL,17,Fand the Somerset Maternity and
OL,18,FNeonatal Voices Partnership to ensure
OL,19,Fthat pregnant women, birthing people
OL,20,Fand their newborn babies receive the
OL,21,Fcare and support they need."
