OL,7,F"We are committed to providing safe,
OL,8,Fhigh quality and sustainable services
OL,9,Ffor those who need them, but we must
OL,10,Faddress these concerns and need the
OL,11,Ftime and space to do this. I apologise
OL,12,Fagain to anyone who is affected by
OL,13,Fthese changes."
OL,15,F'Families in Yeovil deserve more'
OL,17,FAdam Dance, The MP for Yeovil, said in
OL,18,Fa statement the sudden closure was
OL,19,F"deeply unsettling and unacceptable".
