OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"I am extremely concerned by the
OL,8,Fdecision to close Yeovil Maternity
OL,9,FUnit ` even if the Trust says it is
OL,10,Ftemporary", the statement read. Like
OL,11,Fmany people across our community, I
OL,12,Ffind this deeply unsettling and
OL,13,Funacceptable."
OL,15,F"I have directly asked senior figures
OL,16,Fat the Trust for reassurance that the
OL,17,Fservice will reopen after six months `
OL,18,Fand they have been unable to give it.
OL,19,FThat's simply not good enough.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
