OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"Families in Yeovil deserve more than
OL,8,Fvague promises ` they deserve answers,
OL,9,Faction, and proper access to care.
OL,11,F"Moving all services to Taunton, where
OL,12,Fstaff have already raised concerns
OL,13,Fabout not having enough capacity to
OL,14,Fmanage their own patient load, is
OL,15,Fdeeply troubling.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
