OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"Expecting that overstretched service
OL,8,Fto safely take on additional cases
OL,9,Ffrom Yeovil is not realistic, and it
OL,10,Frisks putting even more pressure on
OL,11,Fdedicated staff already at breaking
OL,12,Fpoint.
OL,14,F"I've also been contacted by
OL,15,Fconstituents raising serious concerns
OL,16,Fabout longstanding problems within
OL,17,FYeovil Maternity Unit: poor
OL,18,Fmanagement, unsafe working conditions,
OL,19,Fand how staff have been treated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
