OL,3,CHospital's maternity unit to close
OL,4,Camid safety concerns over care of
OL,5,Cbabies
OL,7,F"These cannot be swept under the rug `
OL,8,Fthey must be addressed openly and
OL,9,Furgently. This isn't just about
OL,10,Fbuildings and services.
OL,12,F"It's about trust ` and right now,
OL,13,Fthat trust has been badly damaged. I
OL,14,Fwill keep pushing for a full
OL,15,Fexplanation from Somerset NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust and NHS Somerset, and
OL,17,FI won't stop demanding a clear plan to
OL,18,Frestore safe, local maternity care in
OL,19,FYeovil. Our community cannot afford to
OL,20,Flose this service for good."
